## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="5fb2f-103"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> 컨트롤은 다음과 같은 기능을 제공 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5fb2f-103">The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> control provides the following capabilities:</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="5fb2f-104">**탐색**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.NavigateToStream%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.NavigateToString%2A>및 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Refresh%2A></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5fb2f-104">**Navigation**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.NavigateToStream%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.NavigateToString%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Refresh%2A>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="5fb2f-105">**탐색 수명**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigating>하십시오 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigated>, 및 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted>합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5fb2f-105">**Navigation Lifetime**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigating>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigated>, and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="5fb2f-106">**탐색 저널링**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.CanGoBack%2A>를 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.GoBack%2A>합니다 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.CanGoForward%2A>, 및 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.GoForward%2A>합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5fb2f-106">**Navigation Journaling**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.CanGoBack%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.GoBack%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.CanGoForward%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.GoForward%2A>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="5fb2f-107">**WPF/HTML 상호 운용성**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%2A> 하 고 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.ObjectForScripting%2A>, 및 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Document%2A>합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5fb2f-107">**WPF/HTML Interoperability**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.ObjectForScripting%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Document%2A>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="5fb2f-108"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> 보안 제약 조건에 의해 바인딩된 합니다 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] 애플리케이션을 호스팅하는 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser>:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5fb2f-108"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> is bound by the security constraints of the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] application that is hosting the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser>:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="5fb2f-109">때 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> 완전 신뢰에서 호스트 되 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] (독립 실행형 애플리케이션, 예를 들어), 애플리케이션 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> 호스트할 수 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] 모든 위치에서 문서.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5fb2f-109">When <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> is hosted by a full-trust [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] application (a stand-alone application, for example), <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> can host [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] documents from any location.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="5fb2f-110">때 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> 부분 신뢰에서 호스트 되 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] 애플리케이션 (을 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xbap-md.md)]예를 들어), <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> 문서를 호스팅할 수 있습니다 **원본 사이트** 애플리케이션 데이터 파일.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5fb2f-110">When <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> is hosted by a partial-trust [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] application (an [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xbap-md.md)], for example), <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> can only host documents that are **Site Of Origin** application data files.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5fb2f-111">자세한 내용은 [WPF 애플리케이션 리소스, 콘텐츠 및 데이터 파일](~/docs/framework/wpf/app-development/wpf-application-resource-content-and-data-files.md)을 참조하세요.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5fb2f-111">For more information, see [WPF Application Resource, Content, and Data Files](~/docs/framework/wpf/app-development/wpf-application-resource-content-and-data-files.md).</span></span>  
  
