## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="5fb2f-141">호출 하는 경우 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.GoBack%2A> 를 다시 탐색할 문서가 없는 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> 탐색이 수행 되지 않습니다 및 예외가 throw 됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5fb2f-141">If you call <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.GoBack%2A> and there are not any documents to navigate back to, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> does not perform a navigation and an exception is thrown.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5fb2f-142">해야 할 경우에 값을 검사할 수 있습니다는 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.CanGoBack%2A> 속성을 다시 탐색할 문서가 있는지 여부를 확인 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5fb2f-142">If you need to, you can inspect the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.CanGoBack%2A> property to determine whether there are documents to navigate back to.</span></span>  
  
   
  
