 <span data-ttu-id="5fb2f-179">다음은 스크립트에서 호출 되는 함수를 구현 하는 문서가 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)]합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5fb2f-179">The following is the document that implements the script functions that will be called from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span></span>  
  
